== Description ==
{{Description|A large, aggressive predator with mottled brown and green skin, known for its sharp teeth and oddly fierce fighting behaviour when hooked. They can be found in ocean water near Snowcap during the day. They are especially active near the water-side enterance of Snowcap Cave.|Bestiary Entry}}

